---
---

<section class="about" id="nosotros">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-image">
        <div class="image-frame">
          <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=600&q=80" alt="Oficina del estudio jurídico" />
        </div>
        <div class="experience-badge">
          <span class="badge-number">20+</span>
          <span class="badge-text">Años de<br/>Experiencia</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-content">
        <p class="section-subtitle">Sobre Nosotros</p>
        <h2 class="section-title">Un Estudio Comprometido con la Justicia</h2>
        <div class="section-divider"></div>
        <p>
          Fundado en Lima en 2005, <strong>Mendoza & Asociados</strong> es un estudio jurídico
          dedicado a brindar soluciones legales efectivas con los más altos estándares
          éticos y profesionales.
        </p>
        <p>
          Nuestro equipo de abogados altamente calificados combina un profundo conocimiento
          del marco legal peruano con una visión estratégica orientada a proteger los
          intereses de nuestros clientes.
        </p>
        <div class="about-features">
          <div class="feature">
            <span class="feature-icon">✓</span>
            <span>Atención personalizada a cada caso</span>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <span class="feature-icon">✓</span>
            <span>Equipo multidisciplinario</span>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <span class="feature-icon">✓</span>
            <span>Confidencialidad absoluta</span>
          </div>
          <div class="feature">
            <span class="feature-icon">✓</span>
            <span>Resultados comprobados</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="#contacto" class="btn-gold">Conozca Más →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    padding: 7rem 2rem;
    background: var(--color-white);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-image {
    position: relative;
  }

  .image-frame {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .image-frame::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -15px;
    left: -15px;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-gold);
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .image-frame img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 450px;
    object-fit: cover;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    filter: grayscale(0.2);
  }

  .experience-badge {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -20px;
    right: -20px;
    background: var(--color-primary);
    color: var(--color-white);
    padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
    z-index: 2;
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .badge-number {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .badge-text {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    margin-top: 0.25rem;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .section-divider {
    width: 50px;
    height: 2px;
    background: var(--color-gold);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-content p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }

  .about-features {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin: 1.5rem 0 2rem;
  }

  .feature {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .btn-gold {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-gold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    transition: color 0.3s;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-gold);
    padding-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .btn-gold:hover {
    color: var(--color-secondary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .image-frame img {
      height: 300px;
    }

    .experience-badge {
      right: 10px;
      bottom: -15px;
    }
  }
</style>
